@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.29) + (v0 + 0.51 * v0 + 0.74)) - v0)
    v1 = v0
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.93 + tmp + 0.26) - (v1 + 0.70 / v2 + 0.25)) / wp.cos(0.59))
    data[tid] = v0
